&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New hire stock equity (RSUs) and employee stock purchase plan (ESPP)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Continuous professional development, product training, and career pathing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An inclusive company culture, able to join our Community Guilds and Inclusion Talks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Benefits and Growth listed above may vary based on the country of your employment and the nature of your employment with Datadog.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
